title: [Vornavian Coast, Coastal Woods]
description: A steep bank follows the path to the east here, sporting bushes and small trees that grow on the incline.  On the rock formations which protrude from the leaves covering the incline, several birds of prey have seemingly taken posts, eyeing the path suspiciously.

A steep bank follows the path to the east here, sporting bushes and small trees that grow on the incline.  On the rock formations which protrude from the leaves covering the incline, dozens of crows have seemingly taken posts, eyeing the path suspiciously.
